          "text": "Performance agent completed with excellent findings. Top insights: the `query.h` → `predicate.h` include chain is the biggest compile-time bottleneck, and the AST→string→AST round-trip in `query_map` is an unnecessary architectural inefficiency worth fixing. Waiting for remaining 9 agents...",
